WEBVTT

00:00.334 --> 00:02.586
- Previously on Underground...
- Rosalee?

00:02.628 --> 00:03.596
There's one man I know motivated

00:03.628 --> 00:04.696
to pluck the petals

00:04.729 --> 00:06.164
off the Black Rose.

00:06.197 --> 00:08.334
Who among you is feeling bricky tonight?

00:08.366 --> 00:09.667
I seen you.

00:09.700 --> 00:11.336
You're still the snake of a slave driver

00:11.369 --> 00:13.366
you was when you left Macon.

00:13.400 --> 00:18.518
Those who make peace
impossible make violence inevitable!

00:19.877 --> 00:20.912
You got chillun?

00:20.946 --> 00:22.615
They were the best thing in my life.

00:22.647 --> 00:24.182
Little girl ran away.

00:24.215 --> 00:25.450
Just kill yourself.

00:25.484 --> 00:28.653
Go, go! Come on. We got you.

